  "title": "🔥Engagement Catalyst (Sales & Marketing Executive)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br />Join our international outsourced sales and marketing company and work with brands across multiple industries. This role offers real-world exposure, personal development, and the chance to be part of a high-energy, people-focused team.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Represent brands at events, roadshows, and campaigns</p></li><li><p>Engage directly with customers and business partners</p></li><li><p>Develop communication, presentation, and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the team to meet campaign goals</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Comprehensive training and ongoing mentorship</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience in face-to-face engagement</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives, weekly pay, and recognition programs</p></li><li><p>Clear pathways for career advancement and leadership opportunities</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for local and overseas exposure</p></li><li><p>Supportive and energetic team culture</p></li></ul><p><strong>Who Should Apply:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates, ORD personnel, and individuals exploring a career switch</p></li><li><p>Motivated, outgoing, and eager to grow in a fast-paced environment</p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply now to kickstart your career with us!</strong></p>",
